@startuml Time_Sync_from_Internet
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam BoxPadding 10

title Time Sync from Internet Sequence

participant "User" as User
participant "Browser" as Browser
participant "app.js" as AppJS
participant "MQTT Broker" as MQTT
participant "ESP32" as ESP32
participant "STM32" as STM32
participant "DS3231" as DS3231

User -> Browser: Click "Sync from Internet"
activate Browser
Browser -> AppJS: Click event
deactivate Browser
activate AppJS

AppJS -> Browser: Get current browser time\nnow = new Date()
activate Browser
Browser --> AppJS: Timestamp (ms)
deactivate Browser

AppJS -> AppJS: Convert to Unix timestamp\ntimestamp = now.getTime() / 1000

AppJS -> AppJS: Update time picker state\ntimePickerYear = now.getFullYear()\ntimePickerMonth = now.getMonth()\ntimePickerDay = now.getDate()\ntimePickerHour = now.getHours()\ntimePickerMinute = now.getMinutes()\ntimePickerSecond = now.getSeconds()

AppJS -> Browser: renderCalendar()\nHighlight current date
activate Browser
deactivate Browser
AppJS -> Browser: updateTimeDisplay()\nShow HH:MM:SS
activate Browser
deactivate Browser

AppJS -> AppJS: Add UTC+7 offset\ntimestampWithOffset = timestamp + 7*3600

AppJS -> AppJS: Build command\n"SET TIME {timestampWithOffset}"

AppJS -> AppJS: Check isMqttConnected

alt MQTT Connected
    AppJS -> MQTT: Publish(stm32Command,\n"SET TIME X", qos=1)
    activate MQTT
    
    MQTT -> ESP32: Forward command
    activate ESP32
    deactivate MQTT
    ESP32 -> STM32: UART transmit\n{"cmd":"SET TIME","value":X}
    activate STM32
    deactivate ESP32
    
    STM32 -> DS3231: I2C write\nSet RTC registers\nyear, month, day,\nhour, minute, second
    activate DS3231
    
    DS3231 --> STM32: Write complete
    deactivate DS3231
    STM32 -> STM32: Update local time variable
    
    STM32 -> ESP32: UART confirm\n{"status":"OK","cmd":"SET TIME"}
    deactivate STM32
    activate ESP32
    ESP32 -> MQTT: Publish(systemState)
    activate MQTT
    deactivate ESP32
    MQTT -> AppJS: Confirmation
    deactivate MQTT
    
    AppJS -> AppJS: addStatus("Time synced from internet:\n{datetime} (UTC+7)")
else MQTT Not Connected
    AppJS -> AppJS: addStatus("ERROR:\nMQTT not connected")
end

AppJS -> AppJS: Update local device clock\ndeviceClockMs = timestamp * 1000\ndeviceClockSetAtMs = Date.now()

AppJS -> AppJS: startDeviceClockTicker()

loop Every 1 second
    AppJS -> AppJS: Calculate display time\nelapsed = Date.now() - deviceClockSetAtMs\ndisplayTime = deviceClockMs + elapsed
    AppJS -> Browser: Update #footerTime\nFormat: HH:MM:SS
    activate Browser
    deactivate Browser
end

AppJS -> User: Time synchronized
deactivate AppJS

@enduml